fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.endpoint

Class TypeAdaptorGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • fun.connor.lighter.compiler.generator.endpoint.TypeAdaptorGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Expression, Statement, TypedElement

    public class TypeAdaptorGenerator
extends java.lang.Object
implements Expression
    Java source code generator for TypeAdapter. This generator can represent instances from any source. The source expression will be duplicated for each piece of code generated using this generator.
